## Project Overview
This is a customized version of the AstroWind template - a high-performance website template built with Astro 5.0 and Tailwind CSS. The project is named "STEFFI" and is deployed to GitHub Pages.

## Key Information
- **Framework**: Astro 5.0 with static site generation
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS with custom theme support (currently set to light:only)
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **Package Manager**: npm
- **Node Version**: 18.17.1+ | 20.3.0+ | 21.0.0+

## Repository Details
- **GitHub Repository**: marcgarnica13/astrowind
- **Live Site**: https://marcgarnica13.github.io/astrowind
- **Base Path**: /astrowind (configured for GitHub Pages)

## Development Quick Start
```bash
npm install       # Install dependencies
npm run dev       # Start dev server at localhost:4321
npm run build     # Build for production
npm run preview   # Preview production build
```

## Code Quality Commands
```bash
npm run check     # Run all checks (Astro, ESLint, Prettier)
npm run fix       # Auto-fix ESLint and Prettier issues
```

## Deployment
The project is configured for GitHub Pages deployment via GitHub Actions. Pushing to the `main` branch triggers automatic deployment.

## Project Status
- Multiple pages have been modified (see git status)
- New CV PDF asset added
- Policies page created
- All changes are uncommitted

## Key Features
- SEO optimized with sitemap generation
- Blog system with categories and tags
- Image optimization with Astro Assets
- Analytics integration ready
- Dark mode support (currently disabled)
- Responsive design with RTL support